text: Bang Chan. As Iâ€™ve frequently noted, I have been a K-Pop fan for almost a decade but I have never seen somebody like you in the musical field before. What you have been and are capable of, is absolutely untouchable and Iâ€™ve learned that there is nothing that can take the sincerity and passion out of your character. I will say, despite being a long-time fan of K-Pop, I didnâ€™t become a Stay until the just a few years ago. I donâ€™t know how I went so long without knowing or supporting Stray Kids sooner, but I am completely and utterly thrilled to be a Stay now. To this day I wouldnâ€™t know about Stray Kids if it werenâ€™t for the Stay. I heard so much conversation among the fans of Stray Kids about how fearless of a leader you were, and I became curious. Over the course of those few years, I have spent my free time, which I lately have a lot of, getting to know you and your members. It started with liking a few songs, but then Stay, who talk with so much praise about you and your members, convinced me to see what was lying beneath the meaning of your music. I began to watch Stray Kids content whenever and of whatever I could, and I gradually fell more in love with your performance and personality overall. I have come to know how passionate and dedicated you are and have always been to music and performing. Even before Stray Kids was officially formed and debuted, you had music in your heart and I can see that clearly every time that you go on stage with your members. Not only do you have a naturally beautiful voice evident of vocal capability and strength, but your dancing skills are rigid and flawless beyond words. Your presence on stage is nothing less than inspirational and you ground and center your members in a way that Iâ€™ve never seen before. You always bring everyone together and emit unity on and off the stage. Outside of your musical performances, however, I have gotten the pleasure of getting to know you and your personality. I donâ€™t even really know where to start by how touched I am at the positive impact you have already made on this world despite still having so much more left to say. Before I became a Stay, I didnâ€™t know much about what Stray Kids had gone through to get where they are now; and I didnâ€™t know just how much you went through either. However, the loving Stay introduced me to how hard you worked individually to keep your membersâ€™ heads above water through the rigorous days of training, performing, and other events that swarmed you. I was, and still am absolutely mesmerized at what you have accomplished to make this group possible, and successful beyond its comprehension. Thanks to the Stay, I know that before Stray Kids even debuted, you formed an unbreakable and unique bond with each of the members as well as one together as a whole. You lift your members up with the emotional and motivational weight of all the words that youâ€™ve ever said to them. To know that there would be no Stray Kids without you makes me love you in a manner that is simply indescribable. I know that I, your members, and the Stay have so much respect and admiration for you because of everything that youâ€™ve done and overcome in just the beginning of your musical journey. I have gotten the honor of seeing at least some of the groupâ€™s history and how it came to be, and seeing how you were a huge part of that makes me appreciate having you in my life more than I did before. You have single-handedly helped carry this group to victory and done so much to ensure that you stay together. You have always kept your promise that you, in words that I once heard you say, â€œDonâ€™t leave anybody behind.â€ On top of leading your group to all of its success and glory, your are also humble and kind and always put them first. You sacrifice so much for your music, your members, and Stay and we recognize how hard you work day in and day out. You are so funny, clever, and know not to take life too seriously. At the same time you are professional, intelligent, respectful, and wise beyond your years. You are every bit qualified to be the leader that you are and I hope you never doubt your capability of doing that because Stay have seen you build something beautiful with your own two hands from the ground up. You never gave up even when the world encouraged you to and from that I find so much inspiration that I donâ€™t even know how how to thank you. All I do know is that your family and parents are the most proud of you and love you more than any of us do. I canâ€™t even imagine how strong they think you are for what youâ€™ve created. I donâ€™t want to put any more pressure or a burden on you, but so much would crash and burn without you and I hope that our love and support is enough to lift you up through your darkest times. You deserve so many blessings and praise. I just hope that you know your efforts are being recognized every second and that Stay, your members, and your family love you beyond words. I canâ€™t thank you enough for everything that youâ€™ve already done. You make Stay and your members feel so valued and desired and I know that only you can do that. I canâ€™t wait to see what you do next because I know that I couldnâ€™t leave you or stop supporting you if I tried. On behalf of your friends, Stay, members, and most importantly family, I pray that this birthday is filled with all of those blessings that you deserve and that itâ€™s everything that you desire. I pray that you and your loved ones remain in good good health and good faith, because the world is relying on it in order to fully heal and love each other. Happy birthday Bang Chan, and from the bottom of my heart, we absolutely adore you!! You make Stray Kids all around the world stay!!!

text: Felix. You have to be one of the biggest blessings on this Earth. I know that I crossed paths with Stray Kids for a reason, and I know you were one of those reasons. Before I even knew anything about Stray Kids, I knew about you. Three years ago, when I got my introduction to K-Pop and was beginning to like quite a few groups, I didnâ€™t know much about Stray Kids, but I did know about you. I couldnâ€™t go anywhere without hearing anybody talk about you, and that was what lead me into wanting to find out more about you, and your position in Stray Kids. I came into the fandom blindly, without knowing any of the names of the members, and relied on the Stay to tell me everything I needed to know about you. It was because of the intense loving fanbase that you have that I learned, in only a matter of days, what a rare talent you are. The depth of your voice combined with your passionate vocals is one of the most beautiful sounds I have ever heard. Your rapping and singing abilities are entirely specific to you and are so captivatingly intriguing, that I knew I loved you from the moment I first got introduced to you. You are so flexible with your voice and on the stage; and once I first got notice of how outstanding you are, I couldnâ€™t stop discovering what made you so enticing and lovable. You are so recognized and appreciated for your natural talent that word reached me about how special you are before I even got a chance to know who Stray Kids really were. Since then, I have been a Stay, and I can say that you are an individual that led me to become one. I have never seen someone with such a bright presence and spirit completely dominant on stage and create an environment so mysterious and energetic for so many people. You bring to music what nobody else can, and I am so happy you share that with all of your Stay when you could be doing something else. I see how happy that you make your members, and since I am a relatively new fan, I still have yet to learn everything that Stray Kids has been through in the years that youâ€™ve been active. However, I have already seen how much you have healed your members when they needed you the most and provided for Stay a support system that they can actually believe in. You are such a delight to be around and I get so happy just seeing your face these days, especially with all of the craziness thatâ€™s in the world. You have a strong-willed heart, and you are extremely kind, forgiving, and non-judgmental. I have loved becoming so acquainted with you and appreciating all of your hard work because you deserve it! You do so much for everyone, and I hope you know that you are so loved and Stay are so grateful to you for even the little things that you do every single day! Never give up and I hope you continue to be the person that uplifts Stay and your members! I know that no matter what happens, Stay will always support you and I canâ€™t tell you how much you really mean to all of us. Thank you so much for being such a kind and loving human being, and for accepting me and so many people into your family as Stay! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future. On behalf of your friends, members, Stay, and most importantly, your family, I want to wish you the most entertaining and enjoyable birthday ever!! Felix, have fun, PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE, stay safe, Happy, Birthday, and WE LOVE YOU!!!

text: Seungmin, I would like to wish you an early happy birthday, as the time is drawing close. My introduction to Stray Kids was unique in that the reason I decided to support it was because of the fans. I have been a K-Pop fan for almost a decade, and I have come to support many groups. However, becoming a Stay was a new experience for me because it was the first time that I joined a group because the love from the fans was so strong, I knew I needed to be a part of it. I learned about each Stray Kids member one at a time, and what I learned and admired very quickly about you was your individuality. Every member stands out for their own reasons, but your charm is retaining your individuality and independence while still being a part of something bigger. I became an official Stay two years ago, and since then I have gotten to see how well you blend in with your members. You are such a valued member of Stray Kids, that we canâ€™t see them existing without you. Youâ€™ve also created a journey of personal growth and development both musically and personally and I have felt so connected to you since Iâ€™ve become a Stay. Your personality is so enticing in that sometimes you can be quiet and shy, but other times you are very vocal and humorous with your members. Itâ€™s very powerful that you can be so sweet and naturally kind-hearted without saying any words sometimes, while other times, being open and direct about how you feel. I can see how much your loving personality has impacted your members, because Iâ€™ve never seen them happier than when you spend time with them. You are always making your members laugh and motivating them just by putting one smile on their face. I feel so inspired watching you build such a trustworthy relationship with them and want to be at least half as generous as you. I know that your members are so thankful for you everyday and couldnâ€™t be anywhere near as successful without you. I have never heard a fanbase talk so highly and frequently of a member in the way that they honor you. I always hear Stay talking about how gentle and sweet you are; and how much positivity and love you bring to the world wherever you go. Stay talk about your rare, emotion-based, and versatile voice that captivates everyone into your performance. They talk about the flawless and effortless dancing that you work so hard to share with us and spoil us with on every stage. They talk about your overall professional and inspirational performance on stage that leaves every Stay wanting to spend more time with you. Iâ€™ve heard so much about how beloved you are Seungmin, and once I became a Stay, I am seeing for myself how much you are adored all over the world. Not only by Stay, but the loving influence that you have on your members makes them and everyone that you meet a kinder and more loving person. Stay praise and speak so highly of you, that I canâ€™t say Iâ€™ve experienced a family this loving toward an idol. I just want you know how much love there is everywhere all around the world for you. You are the reason that so many people lift their heads up and keep going another day, including me. There is so much negativity going on in the world right now, and to have you as a role model and see it not preventing you from sharing more love is making the world even stronger and closer to restoring to its greatness. I really feel like we donâ€™t deserve you sometimes because your genuine strong heart is hard to come across these days. I hope that we can repay you even a little bit of the love youâ€™ve shown us in just a few years since your debut. I know you have worked so hard to be where you are and I donâ€™t even want to pretend to know how much youâ€™ve probably gone through. I just want to take this day, and every day afterwards to recognize and let you become aware of how much I, Stay, and your members really love you. I know that your parents and the rest of your family are prouder of you than any other person and they respond to every action you take with great respect, understanding, and love. Your members and family are so lucky to have you and I know that are thankful and appreciative of you every day. Thank you so much for sacrificing more than we know just to make us happy even a little bit. On behalf of your friends, members, Stay, and loving family, I hope that the love that you have given to this world is given back to you on this special day and every day in your future. Please surround yourself by the people that love you most, and let the love that we have for you give you the most fulfillment! I wish you nothing but happiness for you and your loved ones, and I pray that you all stay safe. Happy birthday Seungmin! author: @inalake_
text:
random things i noticed: (from an intermediate dancer's perspective)
0:08 i just KNOW that was an annoying arm position for everybody, especially hyunjin
0:13 in just this formation you can clearly see everybody's different dance styles, like it looks the same if you dont pay attention but if you do it's really cool
0:16 ok the balance for here would have taken me FOREVER to get. props on that, not a trace of a stumble with the knee push thing.
0:20 here again you can see the difference in style if you slow it down a bit
0:27 the way that han, hyunjin, and felix are all using their centre of balance here is really cool - not to mention, felix is on the balls of his feet pretty much the entire move. like, WOW.
0:30 i just wanted to mention how gracefully lee know did the woah here thats all
0:31 the sharpness is EVERYTHING here, and that move is a really good example of how you can be light on your feet and still execute moves sharply (bc they switch standing legs twice shortly after, so they can't get too grounded)
0:35 you're probably gonna see me say this a lot if u read this entire thing, but THE JUMPS? it's so cool - they're barely getting off the floor so that they can keep moving, but they're extending their body so it looks like they're going higher. they did this in miroh too, they just tucked in their legs to make it seem like they were jumping a lot higher.
0:43 IN got up on his knee? why? i mean it looked amazing, but why would u bruise ur knee here? idk if the dance floors are different in this studio, but in mine i avoid taking knees at ALL COSTS. props to IN if he has been practicing it like that too cause jesus that hurts.
0:48 its the conscious amount of swag that they're putting into this walk that's getting me - everybody's walking heel ball toe to the EXTREME
0:51 i've tried this so many times - how on earth do they travel? well, i finally know. THEY'RE PICKING UP ONE FOOT. WHY WOULDN'T THEY?? idk why, but ive been learning this as a shoe stuck to floor thing. sigh.
0:56 if you pay VERY close attention to everybody's hands here you'll notice that none of them are the them are the same, so another subtle style difference that i feel is worth mentioning. (for example, Bang Chan's hands are in a very gymnastics-y pose, whereas IN's are blades, and... man idk what han is doing with his hands but go off)
0:58 ive been waiting for a moment to talk about this too - everybody, but especially IN, uses their plier really well here - this is a moment where IN has to jump high and far, and you can see that he pliers slightly more than everybody else to do so. And Changbin, who jumps a little lower and travels less only really pliers one of his legs.
1:04 Hyunjin starts turning slightly sooner then everybody else, to through thorough bullsh*ttery i have decided is because he either a) just does that normally, or b) is doing that because he's center

author: @h-playwithmyhart.4806
text: Changbin. Iâ€™m so fortunate to be able to celebrate your birthday with the rest of Stays. I would like to talk about your musicality. Iâ€™ve never heard anybody rap like you, and I know I wonâ€™t hear anybody rap like you for the rest of my life. You have this growl, this grit, that is enough to supply every word you say with the perfect amount of power and character that it needs. No matter what the circumstance is for your song, you retain this originality and this sound that nobody else has. The connection between the raps you create and your execution of them is simply seamless.  Your lyrical style is mesmerizing, and watching these musical ideas pop into your head like second nature is truly astonishing. You can also sing beautifully as well, and the rough texture of your voice gives you this edge that lights up all of your lines. It is rare to see somebody be able to master both singing and rapping, and the unique sound of your voice allows for you to become limitless through both. You are also an incredibly skilled dancer. Your moves are so natural, and watching you feels surreal because you become so immersed in your movement. You absorb all of these choreographies, and then interpret them in such a realistic and emotional way. You have so much power and when you dance, yet you have the right amount of control to give off just the perfect amount of expression. You give care to each little gesture, and treat each move with such delicacy. It is a journey from start to finish when you dance, and you take all of us with you without missing a single detail along the way. Overall, you are one among other artists that sincerely represent our generation and capture its essence. Your innovation and relationship with music are so complex and clear at the same time. You are young, but as you become older and more experienced, there is no telling what youâ€™re already curious and inventive mind will supply to the world. Your impact on music and your Stay will be timeless. At the same time that I love your musicality, I love your personality as well. I first noticed that you are so laid-back and have this calming demeanor. You are also unexpectedly hilarious. You make jokes in moments where nobody anticipates and you can change the entire mood of a situation in mere seconds. You are so humble, and place those around you before you no matter what the circumstances. Though I have never met you in person, you have to be one of the best people to be around and I know that your members know this better than anybody else. You really hold your team down, and together, and always find a way to make sure everybody feels included. It has only been a short time since Iâ€™ve known you, but I saw almost instantly how your members individually love and cherish you in their own special way. You bring the excitement and thrill of life to them wherever and whenever they need it. You have the biggest heart. You have stood your members up time and time again and pointed them in the right direction if ever they forget what they are chasing after. You are somebody they can lean on through all instances in their life; and have become their brother. We all know that you provide your members with a love that they could not get from anybody else. Though they are all different, you find a way to embrace this and form a sacred relationship with each of them. I know that they will continue to grow and develop, but only with you by their side to guide them through it all. They will continue to be the best versions of themselves and there is nothing that can hold them back because you believe in them with all of your heart and soul. Your love will always trail them and aid them for the rest of their lives. Thank you for raising them, and changing their lives forever so that they can lead the fullest life possible. I want to personally thank your family and parents for raising you and helping you become the aspiring young man you are today. I know how much your family means to you, and you have firsthand showed us what they mean to you and how you spend your time with them. It is clear to see that you already keep this in mind with you at all times, but I just want to say that I hope you can always rely on them in your life when you find you need somebody. When you find yourself having troubles down the line, I hope you can remember the feeling of being with them to restore you to your former state of peace and optimism. Your family loves you more than anybody else on this planet, and I hope you know that when you feel there is nobody who can understand, they will always be there to help you out of any tough situation. They are the most proud of you, will always be the most proud of you, and you honor them with every step you take towards your dream. As Stay, we keep them in our hearts as you do and hope to become as dedicated and authentic through all that we do as they are. Changbin, it is often said that Stay are the luckiest fandom in the world, and I can wholeheartedly agree with that as you are responsible for the truth behind this. You are extremely sensitive and considerate of all of our feelings, and that is perhaps one of the aspects of you that I love the most. You seem to always listen to what we have to say and are even eager to respond to it. When discussing Stay with your members or others, you always have the most original ideas and show us how much you love us through your own eyes. When we chose to become a Stay, you chose us. Your world opened up to us and you invited us to become every bit of a part of you as your members and family.  Similarly to your members, there are Stay from all over the world who come from different backgrounds, and it is only because of you that we are able to come together in unity. I know itâ€™s not always easy to let us in and to see us while youâ€™re in a tough situation, but the fact that you put your fears aside and show up for us every time is the greatest testament of your love for us. You are the first person we turn to when we are down and need cheering up. It is truly the greatest honor getting to be the ones that you work so hard for and trust it all to. You have faith in us when we donâ€™t, and it gives us enough confidence to tackle whatever is thrown at us. Thank you for loving us unconditionally, and being there when nobody else has. Thank you for changing our lives, and being at the heart of the greatest days of our lives. I know that youâ€™ve been through a lot, and youâ€™ve only been active with Stray kids for a few mere years. Iâ€™ve seen firsthand how it took all you had and then some to even debut, and there have been too many struggles since then that youâ€™ve faced. The best that I can do, knowing that youâ€™ve been in these difficult situations more than anybody should be in, is try to imagine how it feels to be in your shoes. I know that itâ€™s been a lot. All that I can say, on behalf of all of your loved ones, that we are so proud of you for making it past all of these moments. You have a heart a gold and always keep your head up even when it feels impossible, and I know that this is the reason why youâ€™ve been able to persevere through all that youâ€™ve been through. Thank you for teaching us that we can do the same, and for having enough ability to force a fulfilled live for your Stay and members a well. We know that you can take charge and make it out of whatever happens in the future. I hope that this birthday makes all of your dreams come true and that you accmplish all that you desire on this special day. I often wonder of when you get to take a break and truly look back on the impact that youâ€™ve had on the world, so I hope that if anything, your special day provides you for the perfect opportunity to do that. I hope you are able to look at the countless hearts that you touch every day around the world in limitless ways, and let that make you feel as loved and honored as youâ€™ve ever felt. I hope that those around you also help you to see how worthy of love and commemoration that you truly are. Please relax today and I hope that you spend every second making precious memories. I hope that this day goes down as one of the greatest youâ€™ve had in a while. You deserve all of the sucess and blessings, and I know that more will only come to you. Thank you for sacrificing so much just to make Stray Kids and several other projects possible. Thank you for suffering through any pain, concern, fear, doubt, isolation, confusion, fatigue, stress, and so much more just to bring us any content at all. I hope that you never feel pressured or obligated to change because you are a rare gem of a human being. The world, and more specifically, your Stay need you just as you are to continue to inspire us and remind us what it is to love others and yourself in daily life. You are beautiful inside and out, and perfect as you are. I hope you remember we always will support you no matter what! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future! Happy birthday Changbin, and we adore you so much!!!!

text: Hyunjin. It was certainly your musicality that drew me to you first. You have such a playful but easy tone which highlights and gives definition to every Stray Kids song. You donâ€™t have fixated or set rapping style. You are very experimental vocally and lyrically and Iâ€™ve found myself charmed by your voice due the versatility of it. I also love your singing style for similar reasons. You are just as diverse of a singer as you are rapper. It is really peaceful and harmonious; and blends perfectly with the rest of your members. I love how you donâ€™t hold anything back when youâ€™re singing and I can really feel the emotion and work that you pour into each line that you sing. Similarly to your singing and rapping, your body knows no limits when you are met with a choreography. You dance with a ferocity and a passion that no other performers can possess. You take each choreography and sincerely make it your own, which is honestly a blessing to watch. When you are dancing, you can be yourself and express your emotions with the beauty of your body movements. You can lose yourself easily into your dance and you are so comfortable and trusting of your own abilities. For this generation specifically, you have transformed music and given new meaning to what it can and should do for people. You are changing the world each day that you continue to share your artistry and dance; and we are so lucky to be alive right now to get to be a part of the history that youâ€™re making. At the same time that I love your music and dance, I love your personality as well. I love that sometimes you keep to yourself, but other times, you are goofy and outgoing. As I mentioned before, you are extremely freeing to be around and those who spend time with you can relax and be themselves in your presence. I know that nobody can attest to these qualities quite like your members. Seven different personalities, and they all love you and cherish you for their own special reasons. Theyâ€™ve looked to you and have modeled their perseverance off of how you strive to not let the difficult times hold you down and prevent you from success. You have opened your heart up to all seven people, although you come from different backgrounds, and that has encouraged them to all to have such a loving relationship with one another. Youâ€™ve had love for them since you began your journey with them and this has establishing a lifelong love that all of you had before you even debuted. You see the beauty and necessity of every single member and constantly remind them how important they are to Stray Kids. There is likely no greater feeling for them than knowing that they have you by their side if they donâ€™t have anything else. The most important takeaway is the time they spend with you and the way you make them feel, and these are both filled with warm memories they can take with them for the rest of their lives. Youâ€™ve already spent some of the happiest and life-changing moments of your life with them, and there is still more to come. The members of Stray Kids, also your brothers and your family, couldnâ€™t have somebody who loves them any more than you do to look after them. You are always so considerate of them and their feelings and respond to them however they need. They are the best versions of themselves because of you and because you love them just the way they are. Now, they can go on to do whatever they aspire to because youâ€™ve encouraged them with that confidence. I want to personally thank your parents and family for raising you and helping you become the person you are today. I know they mean a lot to you, and that you couldnâ€™t be here doing what you are without their love and support. Because of them, you can use your platform to share with the world the same love that they have provided you with your whole life. I hope you never forget that they are always going to be the most proud of you no matter what you do. They love you most in this world and they do so in a way that nobody else understands. Stay love them as you do and we keep them in our hearts as we continue our time with you. We are so grateful to them for bringing you into the world, and for changing the world the same way that you do. Hyunjin, you touch each individual heart of every Stay, and this is easily one of the most charming parts about you. It is in your nature to make each and every Stay feel special, even if you donâ€™t know us personally. You welcome Stay from all around the world with open arms, and I felt as if I was a part of the family my whole life. You are so dedicated to your Stay and this is very apparent in everything that you do, whether it be performing or communicating with us directly. You have so much compassion for Stay and I feel like we are existing in our own separate world with you. Although we all live in different areas across the world, you take us to a place where we can all be one big family together, and it is one of the greatest feelings in the world. What you give to us is irreplaceable, and there could never be another person who helps us see the worth in ourselves the way you do. You also help us love one another. You influence others to treat others with kindness and Iâ€™ve met some of the most heartwarming Stay. I know that you help this family become closer every single day, and you remind us that if we have nothing else, we have each other. You invite us into your heart, the same way that you do your members, and you see qualities in us that we donâ€™t even see ourselves. I know for a fact that there are Stay who only believe in themselves because of you. You also share so much of yourself with us, and this is perhaps one of the biggest ways you can show somebody that you trust. As time goes on, I notice you revealing more of yourself through your music and just through direct conversation with your Stay. You have gotten so personal with us and this lets us know just how much you actually believe in us and trust us to keep these parts of you within our hearts. There is no greater honor than to have you place this vulnerable side of you in our hands, and we want to do the same for you. I know that it is not always easy to do this, so I hope you know that we could never mislead you or betray your trust if we wanted to. You are one of the most generous people we know, and we could not be here giving love to others and to you without the love that you gave us first. I know that youâ€™ve been through a lot, both personally, and professionally, and that your time as an idol has not always been easy or enjoyable. Youâ€™ve been active for some time now, but during your training period alone, youâ€™ve been met with demanding expectations, which many people cannot even say theyâ€™ve undergone. Just as your family is, Stay could not be more proud of you from overcoming your hardships and making it out on the brighter side. Each time you are met with a grueling time or task, thought it make time, you eventually endure through it until the end, and become more experienced. As Stay, I can say we learn so much from how you choose to release stress or convey how youâ€™re feeling through the mediums that provide you comfort.  We are beyond proud of you and continue to learn from you each day. I hope that this birthday makes all of your dreams come true, and you can take the time to truly celebrate who you are as a person. I know it might be difficult to focus on yourself, and if you find this to be the case, I hope you leave it to those who surround you and your admiring fans from all across the world to help you realize how revolutionary of a person you are. You are truly a gifted musician, and a courteous and selfless individual. You deserve this day, and every day that follows, to feel as appreciated as you truly are. I hope that every second is filled with memories that are unforgettable, and that this will be one of the greatest days that youâ€™ve had! Please have fun and celebrate in whatever way you choose, because your Stay will be cheering with you!  Thank you for sacrificing your time, efforts, pain, doubt, fear, tears, emotions, and physical boundaries just to bring us any content at all. For every effort that you put in that you might think is small, a Stayâ€™s mood or day is completely changed for the better. You are blessing to this world and continue to change it every day with how you choose to heal it and the people living in it. I hope you donâ€™t overwork yourself because you are perfect just the way you present yourself to us. We will support you and be there for you for the rest of our lives! I pray that you and your loved ones stay safe, and find happiness and worth in the future. Happy birthday Hyunjin, and we adore you so much!!!!

Receta de hoy: carne Escondidinho

INGREDIENTES
1 kg de papa

500 g de carne molida

200 g de queso mozzarella

aceite de oliva

1 cebolla

1 diente de ajo machacado

sal a gusto

pimienta blanca al gusto

aroma verde al gusto

1/2 taza de leche

2 cucharadas de mantequilla

MODO DE PREPARO
Pelar las papas, cortar por la mitad y cocinar con agua y sal.

Una vez cocido, triture las papas, agregue la leche y la mantequilla, revuelva bien hasta hacer purÃ© y reserve.

En una cacerola, agregue 1 llovizna de aceite de oliva, cebolla, ajo y saltee la carne molida.

Sazone con sal, pimienta blanca, olor verde y cocine hasta que el agua que se forma en la olla estÃ© seca.

Forre un plato con la mitad del purÃ© de papas.

Agregue una capa de queso y una capa de carne molida.

Repita el proceso y termine con queso rallado encima.

Hornee por 40 minutos.

author: @may-wq6ir
text:
Today's recipe: Meat Escondidinho

INGREDIENTS
1 kg of potato

500 g ground beef

200 g of mozzarella cheese

olive oil

1 onion

1 clove of crushed garlic

salt to taste

white pepper to taste

green scent to taste

1/2 cup of milk

2 spoons of butter

PREPARATION MODE
Peel the potatoes, cut in half and cook with water and salt.

Once cooked, mash the potatoes, add the milk and butter, stir well until pureed and set aside.

In a saucepan, add 1 drizzle of olive oil, onion, garlic and sautÃ© the ground beef.

Season with salt, white pepper, green smell and cook until the water that forms in the pot is dry.

Line a dish with half the mashed potatoes.

Add a layer of cheese and a layer of ground meat.

Repeat the process and finish with grated cheese on top.

Bake for 40 minutes.

author: @judethefourth336
text:
Thank you so much for uploading this now. We really needed it.

I am so sorry we couldnt give you a win until now. We really tried our best knowing you worked extremely hard and deserved a win because the album is the best of all your releases and you risked a lot deciding to change the title song last minute and I wish my words were better to express how grateful and proud I feel right now for you and for stays. We are really doing our best and trying to go further despite the difficulties. We are really pushing our limits and breaking our past records. I am so sorry that we couldnt win yesterday and today and I hope you can at least feel like you have done enough (BECAUSE YOU HAVE AND WE ARE SO PROUD OF YOU) with the achievements we have gained in these past despite not getting that win.

We still have a few possibilities, so I want to keep being positive and working for you. I hope that next time we can be able to make you win several times. You deserve so much more and I hope that someday we can give you back all the love, support, appreciation and inspiration you give us.

Dont feel discouraged or that you did not good enough. For us, you were the winners. You are always the winners by slowly improving yourselves and showing us the many sides of skz. I am so grateful for being a stay, so I hope you can feel that not even once we have been ashamed of you. Never. We are proud of you. Always. Please, dont overwork yourselves and STAYS I am also really proud of us. We did our best and we should keep this pace until the end of promotions and the next comebacks. This time we couldnt make it (for now) but if we keep working so hard as we did this time, I am sure next time we will top every chart and get many wins.

Cheer up, Stays and Stray Kids. Even in every moment of darkness, there's still some light, some hope and we should never lose our hope
